Bloomberg Photos produced images
throughout 2010 that reflected the news, serving all Bloomberg
platforms and its media clients in print, Internet, mobile and
television.  Stories covered by the team this year included the
Deepwater Horizon oil spill; the Euro crisis in Greece,
Portugal, Spain and Ireland; BHP Billiton Ltd.’s abandoned bid
for Potash Corp. of Saskatchewan Inc.; and Apple. Inc.’s
introduction of the iPad.  Editors:  Mark Beech ,  Bryn Colton .  To contact the editor responsible for this slideshow:
